TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 
$BR
The tangent to the graph of \(f\) through the point \((1,1)\) 
has the slope  \{ ans_rule(20) \} and the

EOT
ANS(num_cmp(2));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 
\(y\)-intercept    \{ ans_rule(20) \}. 
EOT
